<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>2026 GOP Senate Priority Survey</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffff;
        color: #222;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #d1d1d1;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #b20000;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .header img {
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
        border-bottom: 4px solid #b20000;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      th, td {
        text-align: left;
        padding: 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      th {
        background-color: #f1f1f1;
      }
      .button {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #b20000;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #8f0000;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="https://www.myimgcloud.com/6f5037c7-cc7d-4247-9acc-9d73998291cd.png" alt="GOP Header" />
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p><strong>${Recipient.FIRST_NAME},</strong></p>
        <p>Before we finalize the strategy report heading to President Trump, we need your direct input on these key questions:</p>

        <table>
          <tr>
            <th>Question</th>
            <th>Your Answer</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Do you support a full ban on foreign funding in U.S. elections?</td>
            <td>✅ Yes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Should Republicans prioritize flipping the Senate in 2026?</td>
            <td>✅ Absolutely</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Do you trust the mainstream media’s coverage of GOP candidates?</td>
            <td>❌ Not at all</td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <a href="{{survey_link}}" class="button">FINISH THE REST OF THE SURVEY NOW</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
